<h1>HTML Text Formatting</h1>

<p><b>(b)</b>  Bold text</p>
<p><strong>(strong)</strong>  Important text</p>
<p><i>(i)</i>  Italic text</p>
<p><em>(em)</em>  Emphasized text</p>
<p><u>(u)</u>  Underlined text</p>
<p><mark>(mark)</mark>  Highlighted text</p>
<p><small>(small)</small>  Smaller text</p>
<p><del>(del)</del> Deleted text</p>
<p><ins>(ins)</ins>  Inserted text</p>
<p>H<sub>(2)</sub>O  Subscript</p>
<p>X<sup>(2)</sup>  Superscript</p>

<pre>(pre)  Preformatted text</pre>

<p>(p ) Paragraph</p>
<p>(br ) Line break</p>
<p>(hr ) Horizontal rule</p>

